<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٤٦٦٢ -<span class="c5"> حدثنا أبو بكر قال:</span> حدثنا حفص عن سليمان <span class="c2">(أبي)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> عبد اللَّه <span class="c2">(قال)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: قال الحسن: من احتاز <span class="c2">(من)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> رجل مالا <span class="c2">(أو)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> سرق من رجل مالا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وأراد)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> أن يرده <span class="c2">(إليه)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> من وجه لا <span class="c2">(يعلمه)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> فأوصله إليه، <span class="c2">(فلا)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span> بأس.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
